RESIDENTIAL TREE SERVICE, COMMERCIAL TREE SERVICE & MUNICIPALITY TREE SERVICE

Trees "R" Us, Inc. ~ The Right Choice

847-913-9069 • info@TreesRUsinc.com


Specializing in all aspects of tree care ~ residential tree care, commercial tree care and municipality tree care.

 

Whether it is pruning trees to keep them strong and healthy, saving desirable trees or removing problem trees, our teams of professional tree care specialists can accomplish the task efficiently and safely.

 

Stump grinding, tree planting, emergency tree services, dangerous tree removal, tree shaping and trimming, and mulch and firewood delivery are among our expert services.

 

For quality tree care by professional arborists, please call Trees "R" Us, Inc. Quality and service are our number one priority.

 

 

 

 

 

  • OUR CERTIFIED ARBORISTS

    Our Certified Arborists are highly trained in plant and tree care and have gone through rigorous training to make them the best in their field. Have a tree care question, ask our Arborists. They will help you with your residential tree care questions, commerical tree care questions and even municipality tree care questions.

    <

    >

  • PLANT HEALTH CARE

    Our Certified Arborists are highly trained in plant and tree care and have gone through rigorous training to make them the best in their field. Have a tree care question, ask our Arborists. They are highly qualified in Plant Health Care and in overall residential tree care, commercial tree care and municipality tree care.

    <

    >

  • EMERGENCY SERVICES

    Emergency tree service can be extremely dangerous and should only be left to a professional tree service that has the property training in safety to complete the job.

    Our specialty is emergency tree service. We aim to deliver quick, safe and accurate emergency tree removal and tree trimming at an affordable price. Any day, any time of year, Tree "R" Us, Inc. is on call for you. We offer emergency tree services for residential emergency tree services, commercial emergency tree services and municipality emergency tree services.

    <

    >

  • COMPREHENSIVE RESIDENTIAL AND COMMERCIAL TREE SERVICES

    Tree trimming, cabling and bracing, as well as storm damage are just a few of our most popular requested residential and commercial tree services. Take a look at our tree service page for more information. We are available for both commercial and residential tree work, as well as for municipalities to hire.

    <

    >

  • MULCH SERVICES

    Through our environmentally conscious subsidiary, Organic Solutions, Inc., we are able to offer premium quality organic mulch which include milch delivery, installation and edging. We offer residential mulching and commercial mulching.

     

    Organic Solutions, Inc. was formed as an environmentally conscious solution for Trees "R" Us, Inc. to recycle wood debris.

    <

    >

  • SERVICE AREA

    Trees "R" Us, Inc. provides quality, professional tree care to the Chicago-area suburbs. We provided tree service to area as far as Winnetka, Libertyville, Wauconda, and Hinsdale, just to name a few. Please see our service area page for some additional Chicago suburbs that we serve. We specialize in residential tree service, commercial tree service and municipalities.

     

    We also provide tree service to the suburbs of northern Wisconsin and Indiana.

    <

    >
